{"tid":2486507,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥減重方程式大公開！","createTime":"2021-04-13T02:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T19:43:13.000Z","uid":241832,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b9a505f0b29e3c66357b73aec3534c381997be","tid":2486507,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">一字記之曰：心態</span><br />\n<br />\n減肥po經常上熱門嘅原因係永遠都有罵戰<br />\n健身人士：推重訓<br />\n控制飲食人士：推斷食，生醣，low carbs<br />\n<br />\n對立層面某程度已經貼近黃藍！<br />\n<br />\n每個人都會有一套啱自己嘅方法<br />\n可以係做死一套 ，hybrid又得<br />\n最重要係自己舒服<br />\n可以持之以恆<br />\n<br />\n以下係我少少意見<br />\n<br />\n買個家用磅，有check到體脂嘅，另加一部後備電話，一本簿，一支筆<br />\nmark低早晚體重體脂（家用唔準確唔緊要，reference only），體重用lbs（因為個會易啲見到個上落差，都係嗰句，見到落磅就有心繼續落去），再嚟就係每日除衫鏡影自己身體變化，最後記低自己每日嘅食物（for reference或者平台期嗰啲時候可能有用）<br />\n<br />\n真係overweight嘅唔好介意減水減肌肉<br />\n因為你見到跌磅先會有心繼續<br />\n先冇咁容易放棄<br />\n當體重慢慢落就開始加運動<br />\n此消彼長，磅數慢慢落，運動慢慢加<br />\n（重訓／cardio／both）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家目標都係想身體健康，靚仔靚女<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">加油！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8a7d000456e108cb767c970443240bb1d153d2","tid":2486507,"uid":241832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"原來打得咁認真係冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcc18d579f58023f8f42875719a140f222e0966","tid":2486507,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"推多下推唔郁就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"